               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the donor; doxology (also alternating in red and black letters, e.g., fols. 13va, 14va, 15vb, 39ra); groups of lines alternating with black lines on the incipit page of Texts I, II; groups of lines alternating with black lines in the incipit of each section in Text I; incipit of each section in Text II; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="coloph1">
                     <colophon>
                        <locus target="105rb"/>Fol. 105rb: ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘአፈጸመኒ፡ በኢድልወትየ፡ ዘጸሐፍኩ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወጊጉይ፡ ንዑሰ፡ ዓቅም፡ ኃይለ፡ ማርያም፡ ፲ወ፱፻፳፪ዓመተ፡ ምሕረተ፡ በዘመነ፡ ምንግሥታ፡ ለንግሥትነ፡ አስካለ፡ ማርያም፡ አመ፡ ፱ለወርኃ፡ መስከረም፡ በሰላመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አሜን።<foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                        <note>The scribe Ḫaylä Maryam has completed the Ms. on 9 Mäskäräm 1922 year of mercy (= September 19, 1929 A.D.) during the reign Queen Zäwditu (r. 1916-30; baptismal name ʾAskalä Maryam).</note>
                     </colophon>
                  </msItem>
